## Form.FieldNames property

获取表单上的字段名称列表。

```csharp
public string[] FieldNames { get; }
```

### 例子

```csharp
Form form = new Form("PdfForm.pdf");
string[] fields = form.FieldNames;
foreach(string field in fields)
{
  Console.WriteLine(field);
}
```
